  "body": "<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5929\" src=\"https://kreezcraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/header.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2593\" height=\"858\" />\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5930\" src=\"https://kreezcraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/overview.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2586\" height=\"212\" />This mod adds crowns and silver ore! \n\n&nbsp;\n\n<a href=\"https://kreezcraft.com/justenoughcrowns\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5931\" src=\"https://kreezcraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/promo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2586\" height=\"372\" /></a>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you want a server setup using Just Enough Crowns with zero effort, get a <a href=\"https://kreezcraft.com/justenoughcrowns\">server with BisectHosting</a> and receive 25% off your first month as a new customer using the code kreezxil</p>\n&nbsp;\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5932\" src=\"https://kreezcraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/crown_types.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2586\" height=\"212\" /></h3>\n<h3></h3>\n<h3><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5933\" src=\"https://kreezcraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/crowns.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"902\" height=\"686\" /></h3>\n<h3></h3>\n<h3>Notes</h3>\nEverything should be oreDicted, I made sure to set that flag in the recipes.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3>Items &amp; Recipes</h3>\nSee the <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/just-enough-crowns/screenshots\">Images above for a full list of what this mod adds.</a>\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3>TODO:</h3>\n<ul>\n \t<li>* Convert 1.12.2 version to proper Forge code</li>\n \t<li>* Convert 1.14.4 version to proper Forge code</li>\n \t<li>* Convert 1.15.2 version to proper Forge code</li>\n \t<li>* Convert 1.16.5 version to proper Forge code</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;\n<h3>Permissions:</h3>\nIt's MIT Licensed, so you don't need to ask, just add it and go!\n\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5934\" src=\"https://kreezcraft.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/socials.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2586\" height=\"212\" />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/ngNQjT5\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://discordapp.com/api/guilds/96753964485181440/widget.png?style=banner2\" /></a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/kreezxil\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/cwhDBkE.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/MinecraftModdedForge\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/dWeRuXB.png\" /></a></p>",
